      • withRoleByPublicIdExcludingPermissions

        public RoleBuilder withRoleByPublicIdExcludingPermissions(java.lang.String publicId,
                                                 SystemPermissionType[] excludedPermissions)
        In TestBase tests the database is populated with system data at startup, including the standard set of roles (usually defined in product/config/import/gen/roles.csv). This method allows a user to be created with one of these standard system roles excluding the excludedPermissions, which usually have mnemonic public ids such as "adjuster".
        Parameters:
        publicId - the public id of the role
        excludedPermissions - permissions to exclude
        Returns:
        the modified builder
